{SOUTH cannot respond with a Negative Double on this hand because he has only three 
\Hs.

Instead he just bids his 4-card Major, 1\S.

NORTH shows 4-card support with a minimum opener by bidding 2\S and SOUTH 
has enough strength to bid game.}

